documents.content: Name: Bhuvan Subramani. Title: Bhuvan Subramani - Data Science & Software Engineering Portfolio. Meta Description: Bhuvan Subramani - Data Scientist, AI/ML Engineer & Flutter Developer specializing in data analytics, machine learning, and mobile app development.. About: Transforming data into actionable insights and building intelligent applications that solve real-world problems. Long Bio: I'm Bhuvan Purushothaman Subramani, a results-driven Data Scientist and Software Engineer with a unique blend of analytical expertise and mobile development skills. Currently pursuing my Master's in Data Science at Deakin University, I bring hands-on experience in building AI-powered solutions, predictive models, and user-centric mobile applications. My passion lies in leveraging data analytics, machine learning, and modern development frameworks to create impactful solutions that drive business value and improve user experiences.

Project: HyperScale Retail Command Center. Category: data, ml-ai. Description: Implemented end-to-end Real-Time Analytics on Microsoft Fabric, unifying historical sales and real-time order streams into a Medallion Architecture. Utilized PySpark for ETL and Facebook Prophet to generate accurate 30-day demand forecasts. Delivered stockout alerts in under one minute using Fabric Activator, enabling immediate business action.. Technologies used: Microsoft Fabric, PySpark, Facebook Prophet, Real-Time Streaming, Power BI, Delta Lake, Data Engineering, Time-Series ML. Key Metrics: Alert Latency < 1 Minute, 30 Day Demand Forecast, 100% Automated Pipeline. Link: https://bhuvanps.github.io/Portfolio/Hyperscale/.

Project: Bank Loan Performance Analysis. Category: data. Description: Designed a three-tier Power BI dashboard to monitor $435.8M in loans. Implemented complex DAX measures for MTD/MoM tracking and performance analysis. Achieved 86.2% Good Loan rate by providing data-driven insights on risk exposure and debt consolidation strategy.. Technologies used: Power BI, DAX, Financial Analysis, KPIs. Key Metrics: $435.8M Portfolio, 86.2% Success Rate. Link: https://bhuvanps.github.io/Portfolio/Loan_Analysis_Report/.

Project: Financial Fraud Detection System. Category: ml-ai, data. Description: Built a Big Data Analytics solution in Python processing 1M nodes and 10M edges. Enhanced fraud detection accuracy by 15% and reduced false positives using advanced graph algorithms. Strengthened security measures by identifying complex fraud patterns in transaction networks.. Technologies used: Python, Big Data, Machine Learning, Graph Analytics. Key Metrics: 1M+ Nodes, 15% Accuracy Boost. Link: #.

Project: Liver Cirrhosis Survival Prediction. Category: ml-ai. Description: Developed an SVC multiclass classification model predicting patient outcomes (Death, Transplant, No Transplant). Achieved 85.5% accuracy using feature engineering, class weighting, and cross-validation on clinical data. Provided critical insights for early medical intervention and resource allocation.. Technologies used: Python, SVC, Healthcare, Classification. Key Metrics: 85.5% Accuracy, 3-Class Problem. Link: https://bhuvanps.github.io/Portfolio/prediction/.

Project: Wine Quality Prediction Model. Category: ml-ai, data. Description: Developed ML model in R comparing WAM, WPM, OWA, and Choquet Integral algorithms. Selected Choquet model as optimal after performing feature selection and skewness correction. Delivered comprehensive importance interpretation to understand key quality drivers.. Technologies used: R, Machine Learning, Feature Engineering. Key Metrics: 4 Models Compared, Feature Optimization. Link: #.

Project: Game Theory Solver (R Shiny). Category: data. Description: Created an interactive R Shiny application for solving two-player zero-sum games. Calculates optimal strategies (pure/mixed) and game values in real-time. Features a custom UI and educational content to demonstrate game theory concepts.. Technologies used: R Shiny, Game Theory, Optimization, Interactive UI. Key Metrics: Real-time Solving, Interactive Dashboard. Link: #.

Project: Victoria Green Transit Strategy. Category: data. Description: Formulated a data-driven urban mobility strategy generating $15M in regenerative economy potential. Reduced environmental impact by 25% through smart infrastructure analysis and movement optimization. Proposed actionable steps for sustainable city planning and transit development.. Technologies used: Data Analytics, Urban Planning, Sustainability. Key Metrics: $15M Impact, 25% Emission Reduction. Link: #.

Project: C-Meds: AI Medication Reminder. Category: mobile, ml-ai. Description: Launched AI-powered Flutter app on Google Play, featuring custom reminders and medication tracking. Reduced prescription entry time by 90% via high-accuracy auto-scanner. Coordinated QA testing for multi-device reliability, ensuring a seamless user experience.. Technologies used: Flutter, Dart, AI/ML, Firebase, Mobile. Key Metrics: 90% Time Saved, Multi-platform. Link: #.

Project: E-Cell Sastra Mobile Platform. Category: mobile. Description: Led development and Play Store launch, managing 1000+ event registrations. Implemented networking features that reduced manual communication by 40%. Achieved 500+ downloads and enhanced user engagement through a streamlined mobile interface.. Technologies used: Flutter, Dart, Firebase, Event Management. Key Metrics: 1000+ Registrations, 500+ Downloads. Link: #.

Project: AI Appointment Booking System. Category: mobile, ml-ai. Description: Engineered AI-powered scheduling solution, improving booking efficiency by 20%. Streamlined processes with intuitive UI and seamless platform integration. Collaborated cross-functionally to ensure optimal deployment and user adoption.. Technologies used: AI, Flutter, System Integration, UX Design. Key Metrics: 20% Efficiency Gain, Cross-platform. Link: #.

Work Experience: Software Consultant at RADSTEC (05/2024 – 07/2024). Description: Engineered AI appointment booking solution improving efficiency by 20%. Collaborated cross-functionally for seamless integration.. Highlights: AI Integration, 20% Efficiency Boost, Cross-functional Leadership.

Work Experience: Flutter Development Intern at CUROWEBS, Coimbatore (01/2024 – 05/2024). Description: Designed and launched C-Meds on Google Play. Implemented AI auto-scanner reducing prescription entry time by 90%.. Highlights: Play Store Launch, 90% Time Reduction, AI Implementation.

Work Experience: Technical Coordinator at E-CELL SASTRA (07/2023 – 12/2023). Description: Led mobile app development achieving 500+ downloads. Reduced manual communication by 40% through networking features.. Highlights: 500+ Downloads, 40% Communication Improvement, Team Leadership.
Education: Master of Data Science at Deakin University, Melbourne (Present). Description: Specializing in advanced analytics, machine learning, statistical methods, and data visualization..

Education: B.Tech (Hons) Computer Science & Engineering at SASTRA Deemed University (Graduated 06/2024). Description: CGPA: 8.62/10. Strong foundation in data structures, algorithms, and software engineering..
